PIT|Other ESLint errors that block CI:**
PIT|`react/no-unescaped-entities` — Apostrophes in JSX text (e.g. `Kai's Read`) must be `{"Kai's Read"}` or `Kai&apos;s Read`
PIT|`react/jsx-no-comment-textnodes` — HTML comments in JSX children need `{/* */}`, not `<!-- -->`
PIT|`prefer-const` — `let` variables never reassigned → change to `const`
PIT|Node.js version mismatch (SILENT build failure):** The YVON project builds with Node 22 LTS. Node 20 (the GitHub Actions default) silently fails `next build` — no clear error, just exit code 1. Always
